item.title: US-26 West/US-89 South/US-191 South - Jackson
item.description: Cache Drive at Broadway in Jackson. Turn right on Broadway to continue on US-26 West/US-89 South/US-191 South/US-189 South to Hoback Junction. This is the beginning of US-189 southbound.

item.title: End WY-22 East at US-26/US-89/US-189/US-191
